Parsing JSON is super important. Tell us about this.

00:14:37.300 --> 00:14:39.340
So parsing JSON is a big thing.

00:14:39.580 --> 00:14:44.180
When I first got Pydantic version 2 with the Rust core,

00:14:44.780 --> 00:14:46.240
we were using Surve,

00:14:46.260 --> 00:14:49.060
